        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>Hey everyone, I'm going to take a quick break but I'll be back soon. Feel free to join in by sharing your photos, Vee, Steve, Mike66, Joe, and everyone else. Thanks for joining!</p>
            <ul class="post-meta mb-0">
                <li class="post-date"><i class="uil uil-calendar-alt"></i><span>25-07-2024</span></li>
